{"tid":1595490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"612基金: 正研究方法 加快向「義士」提供金錢援助","createTime":"2019-09-26T05:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:25:30.000Z","uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8af12a372b547bde3abc50ecd2a95b035cd57a","tid":1595490,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"(主要在14:00開始)<br />\n<br />\n612基金:  <br />\n- 612基金係合法基金, 在提供金錢援助的程序上, 被法律限制,<br />\n-已正在研究方法, 簡化和加快批核金錢援助的流程, 令義士們可更快獲得金錢援助. (但又不會犯法)<br />\n- 其中一個考慮中的方案 : 組織新的中介組織, 由中介組織去直接資助義士, 然後由這些中介組織再向612基金 claim返錢.<br />\n<br />\n- 612基金係唔會資助買Gear.  如果612基金直接資助買Gear, 基金會變成犯法<br />\n<br />\n- 616遊行強制為612基金籌款, 所有612基金負擔遊行音響費用, 算係籌款活動的行政費用,<br />\n- 音響費用唔平.  HOCC自己攪露天音樂會, 音響支出都超過100萬.    616遊行音響費用, 其實已經係友情價.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/612Fund/videos/370185667199473/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2Fvideos%2F370185667199473%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=96ff5fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/612Fund/videos/370185667199473/</a>"},{"pid":"dbbbc16f9c9634236fd163412f3e8d64d02512fe","tid":1595490,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"612基金睇左林忌個post?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156231352746121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10156231352746121&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=938cad4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10156231352746121</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/VYjwjfW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYjwjfW.jpg&h=2973683e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86b7da8a166f9fce0e663ebf7955cf17d654109d","tid":1595490,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a